-- Atlantic Tropical Storm Odds Raised to 80% by National Hurricane Center
-- Brian K. Sullivan
-- 2010-06-25T17:58:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/atlantic-tropical-storm-odds-raised-to-80-by-national-hurricane-center.html

          
          
             The National Hurricane Center today
increased to 80 percent the chances that a tropical storm will
develop in the Atlantic by late tomorrow. A weather system that
could become Tropical Storm Alex is now off the coast of
Honduras.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
